      <p>
        My favourite git command is the ls.
      </p>
    <h3>
      Function
      </h3>
      The command lists all files available in a directory.it also shows hidden files and details of these files. some flags or arguments that can be used with it include:
      <ul>
        ls
        </ul>
        <ul>
          ls -a
            </ul>    
      <ul>
        ls -la
      </ul>
